# General rules for AI

- Always use kebab-case for file names.
- Typesafety and linting are a must in this project.
- Use our internal definition pattern when defining new features

## Feature organization

- Schema definition: `/src/server/db/schema/[feature].ts` <-- drizzle schema definition
- Queries: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/queries.ts` <-- drizzle queries
- Mutations: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/mutations.ts` <-- drizzle mutations
- Schema validators: `/src/shared/validators/[feature]-schema.ts` <-- shared validators
- tRPC endpoint: `/src/server/api/trpc/routers/[feature].ts` <-- endpoint for internal use
- REST endpoint: `/src/server/api/rest/routers/[feature].ts` <-- public facing apis
- Page: `/src/app/[locale]/[feature]/page.tsx` <-- server side page with prefetch

## Schema definition

- New schema must be placed in: `/src/server/db/schema/[feature].ts`
- New schema must be exported by: `/src/server/db/index.ts`
- Always use snake_case for table names.
- Run the `./start-localstack.sh` to push and seed the db.
- Update the seed script to add fake data to the table.

[todos.ts](mdc:src/server/db/schema/todos.ts)
[index.ts](mdc:src/server/db/index.ts)
[seed.ts](mdc:src/server/db/seed.ts)

## Queries

- Queries for a given entity must go into: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/queries.ts`

[queries.ts](mdc:src/server/domain/todo/queries.ts)

## Mutation

- Mutations for a given entity must go into: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/mutations.ts`

[mutations.ts](mdc:src/server/domain/todo/mutations.ts)

## Validators

- Schema validators must be placed in: `/src/shared/validators/[feature].schema.ts`
- Use `drizzle-zod` library if necessary to reduce boilerplating.
- Add OpenAPI definitions to schemas
- Be sure to use zod/v4 like in the example
- Generate nuqs search params too

[todo.schema.ts](mdc:src/shared/validators/todo.schema.ts)

## tRPC endpoints

- New trpc apis must be placed in: `/src/server/api/trpc/routers/[feature].ts`
- New trpc routers must be exported by: `/src/server/api/trpc/routers/_app.ts`

[\_app.ts](mdc:src/server/api/trpc/routers/_app.ts)
[todo.ts](mdc:src/server/api/trpc/routers/todo.ts)

## REST endpoints

- New rest apis must be placed in: `/src/server/api/rest/routers/[feature].ts`
- New rest routers must be exported by: `/src/server/api/rest/routers/_app.ts`

[\_app.ts](mdc:src/server/api/rest/routers/_app.ts)
[todo.ts](mdc:src/server/api/rest/routers/todo.ts)

## Page (server side)

- New feature page must be placed in: `/src/app/[locale]/[feature]/page.tsx`
- nuqs must be used to retrieve and parse query params
- tRPC must be used to prefetch data

